
No sophisticated install flow yet...

Requirements:

- standards compliant C++ compiler (recommended: GNU g++)
- standards compliant C++/STL library
- POSIX environment
- GNU regex library

To install it:

- select the options in the Makefile
- type "make"
- copy binary pathplode to your PATH (e.g. /usr/local/bin)

For help:

pathplode --help

